How to make a Greek-themed web game with:

## 1) Project Setup & Foundation
  ✔ Initialize Next.js 14+ project with TypeScript @started(25-06-09 21:16) @done(25-06-09 21:16) @lasted(52s)
  ☐ Setup Tailwind CSS with custom theme for Greek aesthetics @started(25-06-09 21:16)
