    * React Hook Form (forms if needed)
    * Lucide React (icons)

## 2) Game Architecture & Planning
  ☐ Define game concept and core mechanics
  ☐ Create wireframes/mockups for game screens
  ☐ Design game state structure
  ☐ Plan component hierarchy
  ☐ Define TypeScript interfaces for game entities
  ☐ Setup folder structure:
    * /components/game
    * /hooks/game
    * /stores
    * /types
    * /utils/game

## 3) Core Game Components
