  ☐ Create UI overlay components (HUD, menus)
  ☐ Build responsive layout with Tailwind
  ☐ Add Greek-themed styling and animations

## 4) Game Logic & Systems
  ☐ Implement game loop using useEffect/requestAnimationFrame
  ☐ Create collision detection system
  ☐ Build scoring/progression system
  ☐ Implement game state management (playing, paused, game over)
  ☐ Add sound effects and background music
  ☐ Create save/load functionality (localStorage)

## 5) User Interface & Experience
  ☐ Design main menu with Greek mythology theme
  ☐ Create settings/options menu
  ☐ Build game over/victory screens
  ☐ Implement responsive design for mobile
  ☐ Add keyboard and touch controls
